,"tid":2004031,"uid":237425,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"民政專員不提供場地同協助開區議會<br />\n算唔算公職人員行為失當?<br />\n<br />\n算<br />\n我覺得可以搵申訴專員公署"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"係老廉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cae43adb5fa3347806adec4940b57bde56b124","tid":2004031,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc4e537b0f2da25609c22e3bf60b332a20a3c192","tid":2004031,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"中西區人一齊搵民政專員啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"許智峯議員係門口講緊經， 好長氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3612bc63618c0ff0d68dd571102b6cd5a98fc7a2","tid":2004031,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa0514752ae035c4446754bbd2645647b4530eed","tid":2004031,"uid":278570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4477b4bad4173e6c8076a67edd7368e1e1fc3037","tid":2004031,"uid":237425,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"民政專員不提供場地同協助開區議會<br />\n算唔算公職人員行為失當?<br />\n<br />\n算<br />\n我覺得可以搵申訴專員公署"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"有冇得直接私人檢控？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"要搵長洲覆核王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公職人員行為失當罪的主要元素<br />\n************************************<br />\n終審法院在過往案例中，列出構成公職人員行為失當罪的主要<br />\n元素1，包括：<br />\n(1) 一名公職人員；<br />\n(2) 他2在擔任公職期間或在與擔任公職有關的情況下；<br />\n(3) 藉作為或不作為而故意作出不當行為，例如故意忽略或<br />\n不履行其職責；<br />\n(4) 沒有合理辯解或理由；及<br />\n(5) 考慮到有關公職和任職者的責任、他們所促進的公共目<br />\n標的重要性及偏離責任的性質和程度，有關的失當行為<br />\n屬於嚴重而非微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n就上文所述，有關的失當行為必須是故意作出而並非無心之<br />\n失，意指有關公職人員是知道他的行為是違法的，或是故意<br />\n罔顧他的行為有違法之嫌。公職人員在沒有合理辯解或理由<br />\n下故意作出失當行為，須負刑責。<br />\n此外，公職人員的行為即使並不涉及受賄或獲取任何金錢利<br />\n益，也可能會干犯公職人員行為失當罪行。<br />\n簡而言之，該罪行主要針對公職人員濫用他以公職身分所獲<br />\n賦予為公眾利益而可行使的權力、酌情權或職能而作出的失<br />\n當行為。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hksargegu.org.hk/public_html/S%20Topic/CS%20BOOKLET/MIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksargegu.org.hk%2Fpublic_html%2FS%2520Topic%2FCS%2520BOOKLET%2FMIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=07c5a6de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hksargegu.org.hk/public_html/S%20Topic/CS%20BOOKLET/MIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ede951669fc60a1ac112c53ce66ad186b6c8c404","tid":2004031,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61d9373461bbbc5002abab38ba6fc0b7760a8165","tid":2004031,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"區議員圍緊"},{"pid":"37c5caa1928d497ea03bcb1a1437c03aca76513e","tid":2004031,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"218681f5aeb2a0bf7b642fff804248c0a85f5663","tid":2004031,"uid":56624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"建議區議會自己撥款租個新議場，再撥款請人做秘書，直接撇甩港共公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2825c177917910b7f7858df58ef524df010a730","tid":2004031,"uid":72988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"推 煲大佢 咁痴線都無乜人理"},{"pid":"504a36d4548491075b64a0eea647c2bb3252b380","tid":2004031,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4fc0aac713a945eb48d9dc747cafc9ca00f005a1","tid":2004031,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3612bc63618c0ff0d68dd571102b6cd5a98fc7a2","tid":2004031,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa0514752ae035c4446754bbd2645647